body_html: NOTE: This is an identical pull request to one earlier. That has been approved but I was asked to rebase. GitHub was having trouble with the diffs after a rebase, so I took HEAD revision and manually reapplied all changes again and force pushed. I though GitHub would still consider it valid for the pull request. However, it seems I was sorely wrong.
